    "type": "list",
    "content": [
      "Did you miss the Student Vote on Wednesday? There will be a voting station set up in the front foyer at lunch today to get your vote in.",
      "Choir - Soprano and Alto's only today's lunch hour.",
      "Pizza sales - at the canteen at lunch. $3/slice, or 2 for $5.",
      "Lunch - if you need a lunch today, there will be a free option at the concession.",
      "Tennis club - today 4:00- 5:30pm at Anderton Park Courts. Please bring appropriate attire and supplies (I.e. nonmarking shoes, athletic wear, tennis racquet, and water bottle). Please ensure that you are on the TEAMS chat for all the up-to-date information.",
      "Ice bucket challenge pictures - Grads only - do you have pictures of you doing the ice bucket challenge? Please send them to Mr. Green by the end of the day so they can be added to the yearbook.",
      "Volunteers needed for Comox Valley Farmer's Market - all the jobs take place outside. Some of the volunteer tasks include market set up and tear down, sign board artwork, market information booth, kid's activities, parking, special events, recycling program, equipment repair and maintenance, and more. From April to October, The Market takes place at the Comox Valley Exhibition Grounds. Set up starts at 7am, the market runs until 3 pm . From June to September, there is an additional market that takes place downtown Cumberland on Sundays, starting at 8am-2:30pm. Volunteer for as little as 1-2 hours per market. Students can apply directly online at: https://forms.gle/jC42pvAGAEgofnbz6"
    ]
  },
